course.subject: MECH
course.name: Combustion
course.description: Thermodynamics and equilibrium, chemical kinetics, laminar premixed flames, laminar non-premixed flames, turbulent flames, kinetics of pollution formation, gas turbine combustion, condensed phase combustion, flame-flow interactions, internal flame processes, flame stabilization, heat-release dynamics.
course.prerequisites: MECH 2210 AND MECH 2310
